Experiment D2: ancestor-expanded RAG + IC-similarity baseline fairness
Same tasks/splits as reports/confirmatory/ontology_suite.csv (seeds 7/17/23, n_index=2000, n_query=120).
Primary metric: tail (rare) top-5; paired bootstrap of SMA-minus-baseline; Holm across the baseline family per arm.
Ancestor-expanded arms fold the FULL is-a ancestor closure (term names) into BOTH document and query text before ranking.

